allorsBrand.description:
Kahlbacher Machinery is located in Kitzbühel, a tourist town in the Austrian Alps.

Today the company is a full service supplier of snow clearing and winter maintenance equipment with technically superior quality for roads, railways and airports. This optimum quality is ensured through continuous innovation, development of customer-specific solutions, advanced manufacturing techniques and highly trained technical personnel.
The pioneering capability is demonstrated in particular by the numerous domestic and foreign patents gained over the many years.
The realisation of projects starts with design. 3D CAD systems are used to transpose new challenges into reality. All equipment is produced in Austria using the latest production techniques.
